r8w alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85)">It is best to store strips at room temperature. If you live in a warm climate you may keep the strips In a cool dry place, however under normal circumstances, this is not required.</span></p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="2e6a9a9a-7d64-43e7-b9bf-713381cce5c9" class="r-gi7kpa" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="c9fc9c41-9de2-4d62-81fb-3b19a5971190" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R3r32:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-aaiycv"><div data-rid="e936582f-9685-4dcf-9eeb-1de5c52c7ada" class="r-18eikt4 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><h5><strong>Are whitening strips suitable for everyone?</strong></h5></span></div><div data-rid="445e09fa-1f03-4c46-892a-0558f7bdc063" class="r-1wnsyrc" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:100%" class="r-pjbmzn" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R3r32:"><div data-rid="d9ba7108-7633-47de-ba11-eace2d30a364" class="r-8b4x4t"><div data-rid="0f721c23-eae5-441e-bc9f-1655c15a6501" class="r-2euogr alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85)">White strips only work on natural teeth. However, if you have crowns or veneers and have stains in between your teeth, POOOF!® may be effective in removing superficial stains.</span></p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="c1f57262-1438-4e27-9430-fb3d5d45e5c3" class="r-1oxdmmg" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="2e7bc6eb-db89-4325-a238-df5c79aeb741" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R4b32:" tabindex="0" role